net.creativeparkour

Class CPMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.creativeparkour.CPMap

  • public class CPMap
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a CreativeParkour map, with all its properties.
    Parkour maps are cubic.
    Author:
    Obelus
